The paper deals with building chatbots using question answering data from web forums, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). The paper also uses seq2seq models and model selection strategies, which are commonly used in NLP research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
